# Rocq project file for Presburger Boolean Algebra correctness proofs
#
# Verifies that the Presburger NFA construction (presburger.rs) forms a
# Boolean algebra over decidable predicates on Z:
#
#   - Commutativity, associativity of AND/OR
#   - Absorption laws
#   - Complementation (AND/OR with complement)
#   - De Morgan's laws
#   - Distributivity (AND over OR, OR over AND)
#
# Model: predicates as decidable sets over Z, NFA acceptance as set membership.
#
# Reference: Buechi (1960), Bartzis-Bultan (2003)

-Q theories PresburgerProofs

# Source files
theories/PresburgerBooleanAlgebra.v
